195
00:13:50,450 --> 00:13:52,280
What a pleasant atmosphere.

196
00:13:54,340 --> 00:13:56,260
S-S-So what!?

197
00:13:56,260 --> 00:13:57,160
Nothing at all.

198
00:13:57,160 --> 00:14:00,380
The weather is nice. That's all I meant.

199
00:14:00,380 --> 00:14:03,440
I just felt like going for a walk.

200
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:06,340
It's really been too long since I last felt like this.

201
00:14:14,470 --> 00:14:19,890
I've felt so cooped-up every day for so long, I never really felt like laughing.

202
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,060
Water!

203
00:14:53,750 --> 00:14:58,980
You said you'd been by yourself since you were eight, huh?

204
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:00,380
Yes.

205
00:15:00,380 --> 00:15:03,690
