209
00:15:16,970 --> 00:15:18,350
Is she your teacher?

210
00:15:18,350 --> 00:15:20,490
Y-Yeah she is.

211
00:15:20,490 --> 00:15:22,970
Doctorine taught me everything!

212
00:15:22,970 --> 00:15:25,530
Everyone else calls her Dr. Kureha.

213
00:15:25,530 --> 00:15:27,120
Dr. Kureha?

214
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,290
What kind of person is she?

215
00:15:28,290 --> 00:15:30,780
She loves to drink.

216
00:15:30,780 --> 00:15:33,140
And although she's a woman, she looks like a pirate.

217
00:15:33,140 --> 00:15:35,960
And although she looks like a pirate, she's a doctor!

218
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:53,120
