219
00:15:56,470 --> 00:16:00,700
Add these three herbs to the pestle, and then grind them together...

220
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,580
Chopper.

221
00:16:03,680 --> 00:16:04,630
Chopper!

222
00:16:06,860 --> 00:16:08,370
Have you finished with that meadical book yet?

223
00:16:08,370 --> 00:16:10,920
